<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .message-sm {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .course-info {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .course-info table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .course-info td, .course-info th {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .course-info th {
            background-color: #eaeaea;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #4285f4;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .banner {
            background: #00468b;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .motivation {
            background: #e0f0fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .motivation p {
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="banner">
            <h1>Pathshala Order Confirmation</h1>
            <p>Your gateway to educational excellence!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="course-info">
            <h3>Thank you for your purchase. Here are your order details:</h3>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Order code:</th>
                    <td><%= order._id %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Order Date:</th>
                    <td><%= order.date %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Item</th>
                    <th>Qty</th>
                    <th>Cost</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2">Subtotal:</td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2">Total:</td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="motivation">
            <p>Education is not the filling of a pail, but the lighting of a fire. Keep your curiosity alive and your focus unwavering. Every small step counts in your journey towards knowledge and success!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@pathshala.com">support@pathshala.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2023 Pathshala. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
